===Unincorporated territory flags===
{{mono|Country_data}} templates are also available for several organized [[territories of the United States]]. Many of the unorganized territories are either uninhabited or have no indigenous inhabitants, and also do not have unique flags. For those, please use <code><nowiki>{{flagicon|United States}}</nowiki></code>.
